            <title>
                <![CDATA[Curve 創辦人還清 Aave 債務，CRV 自九月中旬已漲三成]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">Curve 創辦人 Michael Egorov 還清了在 Aave 的債務，但目前總計仍抵押了 1.32 億美元的 CRV，有 4,270 萬美元的債務分散於 4 個借貸協議中。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/michael-egorov-to-settle-debt-on-aave#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-65166fe32831d"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-65166fe32831d"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/michael-egorov-to-settle-debt-on-aave/#Curve_%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E6%B8%85%E5%84%9F_Aave_%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%99" title="Curve 創辦人清償 Aave 債務">Curve 創辦人清償 Aave 債務</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/michael-egorov-to-settle-debt-on-aave/#Michael_Egorov_%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%99" title="Michael Egorov 仍有千萬美元債務">Michael Egorov 仍有千萬美元債務</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/michael-egorov-to-settle-debt-on-aave/#CRV_%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B4_04_%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83" title="CRV 一度跌破 0.4 美元">CRV 一度跌破 0.4 美元</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Curve_%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E6%B8%85%E5%84%9F_Aave_%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%99"></span><strong>Curve 創辦人清償 Aave 債務</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>據 Lookonchain 的追蹤，Michael Egorov 已向借貸協議 Silo 存入 6,800 萬枚、價值 3,550 萬美元的 CRV 代幣，並借出 1,077 萬 crvUSD。</p><p>他隨後將 crvUSD 全數兌換為 Tether，償還他最初在 Aave 的債務。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Michael Egorov deposited 68M <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%24CRV&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">$CRV</a> ($35.5M) to <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Silo?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Silo</a> and borrowed 10.77M <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%24crvUSD&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">$crvUSD</a> in the past 2 days.</p><p>Then swapped <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%24crvUSD&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">$crvUSD</a> for <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%24USDT&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">$USDT</a> and repaid the all debt on <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Aave?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Aave</a>.</p><p>He currently has 253.67M <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%24CRV&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">$CRV</a>($132.52M) in collateral and $42.7M in debt on 4 platforms.<a href="https://t.co/stkFvDrlnv">https://t.co/stkFvDrlnv</a><a href="https://t.co/oBQ4yiT9Xs">pic.twitter.com/oBQ4yiT9Xs</a></p><p>— Lookonchain (@lookonchain) <a href="https://twitter.com/lookonchain/status/1706846422304534836?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 27, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Michael_Egorov_%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%99"></span><strong>Michael Egorov 仍有千萬美元債務</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>據此前報導，他在 Curve 遭駭前抵押大量 CRV，借出了 1.02 億美元的穩定幣。</p><p>在駭客事件爆發後，有借貸關係的 DeFi 協議為了防治清算帶來的風險，也相繼提案逼迫 Curve 創辦人盡快還錢。</p><p>相關報導：</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://abmedia.io/is-curve-founders-position-too-big-for-defi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">自己發的幣最好用！Curve 創辦人借款量超 1 億美元，全部用 CRV 抵押且大量出金</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://abmedia.io/curve-finance-crv-liquidation-analysis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">看懂 Curve(CRV) 創辦人清算危機！孫宇晨金援、高獎勵 CRV 池，陸續還款 Aave/FRAX/MIM</a></p></li></ul><p>不過 Michael Egorov 近期的操作成功縮減了將鏈上債務，他總計抵押了 2.5367 億枚 CRV (約 1.32 億美元)，在 Silo、Fraxlend、Inverse 和 Cream 等四個協議中的剩餘債務為 4,270 萬美元。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="CRV_%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B4_04_%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83"></span><strong>CRV 一度跌破 0.4 美元</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>CRV 在 9 月中旬一度跌破 Michael Egorov 在籌錢期間時，透過 OTC 以 0.4 美元兜售的關鍵價位，最低跌至 0.389 美元。</p><p>不過幣價自 9 月 13 日之後也觸底反彈，截稿前價格為 0.52 美元，自低點漲幅 34.9%。</p><figure id="attachment_79942" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-79942" style="width: 912px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-79942 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2-2023-09-28-192144.png?resize=912%2C599&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="912" height="599" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-192144.png?w=912&amp;ssl=1 912w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-192144.png?resize=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-192144.png?resize=600%2C394&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-192144.png?resize=768%2C504&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 912px) 100vw, 912px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-79942" class="wp-caption-text">CRV 30 日走勢</figcaption></figure>
