            <title>
                <![CDATA[支付服務商 Paysafe 單方面暫停幣安歐元入金，趙長鵬：盡速上線替代方案]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">幣安的支付合作夥伴 Paysafe 繼 3 月暫停英鎊出入金後，這次單方面暫停了為幣安用戶提供的歐元入金服務。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/paysafe-o-stop-processing-eur-deposits-for-binance#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-65166fe32edaa"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="list-377408" width="20px" height="20px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999" class="arrow-unsorted-368013"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-65166fe32edaa"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/paysafe-o-stop-processing-eur-deposits-for-binance/#Paysafe_%E5%96%AE%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%B9%A3%E5%AE%89%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E5%85%A5%E9%87%91" title="Paysafe 單方面暫停幣安用戶歐元入金">Paysafe 單方面暫停幣安用戶歐元入金</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/paysafe-o-stop-processing-eur-deposits-for-binance/#CZ%EF%BC%9A%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%B0%87%E7%9B%A1%E9%80%9F%E4%B8%8A%E7%B7%9A" title="CZ：替代方案將盡速上線">CZ：替代方案將盡速上線</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/paysafe-o-stop-processing-eur-deposits-for-binance/#Paysafe_%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E4%B9%9F%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E8%8B%B1%E9%8E%8A%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5%E9%87%91" title="Paysafe 此前也暫停英鎊出入金">Paysafe 此前也暫停英鎊出入金</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Paysafe_%E5%96%AE%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%B9%A3%E5%AE%89%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E5%85%A5%E9%87%91"></span><strong>Paysafe 單方面暫停幣安用戶歐元入金</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p><a href="https://www.binance.com/en/support/announcement/important-updates-for-paysafe-users-7dc31be6889b4fc8ab21292856f38e0f" target="_blank" rel="noopener">幣安公告</a>呼籲 Paysafe 用戶提前採取適當行動，有幾項服務異動：</p><ol><li><p>9 月 25 日 00:00 (UTC) ：暫停 Paysafe 用戶歐元入金</p></li><li><p>9 月 28 日 04:00 (UTC)：暫停歐元交易加密貨幣、自動定投 (非 Paysafe 用戶仍正常)</p></li><li><p>9 月 28 日 04:00 (UTC)：Binance Convert 僅能市價兌換，不能再開限價單</p></li><li><p>10 月 31 日 00:00 (UTC)：用戶需在此前將歐元餘額轉為 USDT，歐元餘額也能出金至銀行帳戶</p></li></ol><p>公告表示，Paysafe 的單方面決定過於突然且莫名其妙，對用戶深感抱歉，用戶仍可以透過信用卡、金融卡以歐元購買加密貨幣。</p><p>不過 KOL <a href="https://twitter.com/DefiIgnas/status/1707304874918969565" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ignas</a> 表示，他的歐元餘額是無法兌換回 USDT 的，幣安 App 似乎已無法辨認歐元餘額。</p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="CZ%EF%BC%9A%E6%9B%BF%E4%BB%A3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E5%B0%87%E7%9B%A1%E9%80%9F%E4%B8%8A%E7%B7%9A"></span><strong>CZ：替代方案將盡速上線</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>CZ 稱這項更動對 Paysafe 的歐元用戶相當重要，替代方案將盡速上線。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">This is an important announcement impacting some EUR / Paysafe users. There should also be replacement fiat channels going live soon. Please stay tuned. 🙏</p><p>Important Updates for Paysafe Users | Binance Support <a href="https://t.co/9XoF4olkjN">https://t.co/9XoF4olkjN</a></p><p>— CZ 🔶 Binance (@cz_binance) <a href="https://twitter.com/cz_binance/status/1707298497936962034?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 28, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Paysafe_%E6%AD%A4%E5%89%8D%E4%B9%9F%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E8%8B%B1%E9%8E%8A%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A5%E9%87%91"></span><strong>Paysafe 此前也暫停英鎊出入金</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>此前報導，今年 3 月時，Paysafe 聲稱英國的加密監管太具挑戰性，決定停止在英國向幣安客戶提供其數位錢包的解決方案。</p><p>幣安自 3 月 13 日起暫停新用戶的英鎊充值和提款，並於 5 月 22 日停止所有用戶的英鎊出入金交易。</p><p><strong>(回顧報導：<a href="https://abmedia.io/20230314-binance-will-suspend-gbp-transactions-by-paysafe" target="_blank" rel="noopener">監管日益嚴峻？繼美元後，幣安再傳暫停英鎊出入金</a>)</strong></p>
]]>
            </description>
