                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="10px" height="10px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.2" baseProfile="tiny"><path d="M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z"></path></svg></span></span></label><input aria-label="Toggle" type="checkbox" id="item-65166fe334e42"></a></span></div><nav><ul class="ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 "><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1" href="https://abmedia.io/binance-sells-russian-unit-to-commex/#CommEx%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%A3%E5%AE%89%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E6%89%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B" title="CommEx，幣安退出俄羅斯前一日才成立">CommEx，幣安退出俄羅斯前一日才成立</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2" href="https://abmedia.io/binance-sells-russian-unit-to-commex/#CommEx_%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E6%89%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%8E%A8%E7%89%B9" title="CommEx 九月才創推特">CommEx 九月才創推特</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3" href="https://abmedia.io/binance-sells-russian-unit-to-commex/#CommEx_%E8%88%87%E5%B9%A3%E5%AE%89%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%B1%E7%A7%81%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E9%9B%B7%E5%90%8C" title="CommEx 與幣安的隱私聲明雷同">CommEx 與幣安的隱私聲明雷同</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4" href="https://abmedia.io/binance-sells-russian-unit-to-commex/#%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E5%85%A9%E8%80%85%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E6%B5%81%E5%8B%95%E6%80%A7" title="社羣質疑兩者共享流動性">社羣質疑兩者共享流動性</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5" href="https://abmedia.io/binance-sells-russian-unit-to-commex/#CommEx_%E5%90%88%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%99%E6%BA%96%E4%BD%8E%E8%90%BD" title="CommEx 合規標準低落">CommEx 合規標準低落</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6" href="https://abmedia.io/binance-sells-russian-unit-to-commex/#CommEx_%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E9%81%B8%E9%A0%85%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C" title="CommEx 支付選項包括被制裁銀行">CommEx 支付選項包括被制裁銀行</a></li><li class="ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2"><a class="ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7" href="https://abmedia.io/binance-sells-russian-unit-to-commex/#%E8%B6%99%E9%95%B7%E9%B5%AC%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%EF%BC%9A%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E9%A1%9E%E4%BC%BC%E6%98%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%86%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97" title="趙長鵬回應：設計類似是為了用戶體驗">趙長鵬回應：設計類似是為了用戶體驗</a></li></ul></nav></div><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="CommEx%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%A3%E5%AE%89%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E6%89%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B"></span><strong>CommEx，幣安退出俄羅斯前一日才成立</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>雖然 CommEx 在 2023 年 9 月 26 日成立，卻馬上被 <a href="https://coinmarketcap.com/exchanges/commex/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CoinMarketCap</a> 計入，但尚未列入排名，也未追蹤 CommEx 的交易量。</p><p>CoinGecko 並未列出 CommEX 相關資訊。</p><figure id="attachment_79903" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-79903" style="width: 1193px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-79903" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2-2023-09-28-133712.png?resize=1193%2C467&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1193" height="467" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-133712.png?w=1634&amp;ssl=1 1634w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-133712.png?resize=300%2C118&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-133712.png?resize=1024%2C401&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-133712.png?resize=600%2C235&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-133712.png?resize=768%2C301&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-133712.png?resize=1536%2C602&amp;ssl=1 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-79903" class="wp-caption-text">CommEx 稱獲得頂級加密創投支持</figcaption></figure><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="CommEx_%E4%B9%9D%E6%9C%88%E6%89%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%8E%A8%E7%89%B9"></span><strong>CommEx 九月才創推特</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>CommEx 於 9 月 26 日宣告正式上線，卻也有在 7 月<a href="https://commex.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/7512437528591-CommEX-Listed-BTC-USDT-ETH-USDT-Trading-Pairs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">宣佈上架</a> BTC/USDT、ETH/USDT 交易對的奇怪公告？</p><p><a href="https://twitter.com/CommEX_com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方推特</a>也顯示 2023 年 9 月才加入。</p><figure id="attachment_79905" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-79905" style="width: 705px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-79905 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2-2023-09-28-140046.png?resize=705%2C486&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="705" height="486" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-140046.png?w=705&amp;ssl=1 705w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-140046.png?resize=300%2C207&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-140046.png?resize=600%2C414&amp;ssl=1 600w" sizes="(max-width: 705px) 100vw, 705px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-79905" class="wp-caption-text">CommEx 上線公告</figcaption></figure><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="CommEx_%E8%88%87%E5%B9%A3%E5%AE%89%E7%9A%84%E9%9A%B1%E7%A7%81%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E9%9B%B7%E5%90%8C"></span><strong>CommEx 與幣安的隱私聲明雷同</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>兩者部分的隱私聲明相似，黑色背景為幣安。</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://commex.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/7496912208527-Privacy-Notice" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CommEx</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://www.binance.com/en/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">幣安</a></p></li></ul><figure id="attachment_79904" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-79904" style="width: 780px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-79904 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/%E9%A6%96%E5%9C%96-2.png?resize=780%2C520&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="780" height="520" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/首圖-2.png?w=780&amp;ssl=1 780w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/首圖-2.png?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/首圖-2.png?resize=600%2C400&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/首圖-2.png?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-79904" class="wp-caption-text">隱私聲明</figcaption></figure><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E5%85%A9%E8%80%85%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E6%B5%81%E5%8B%95%E6%80%A7"></span><strong>社羣質疑兩者共享流動性</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>CommEx 提供了「幣安登入」功能引起廣大社羣質疑，風投 Cinneamhain Ventures 合夥人 Adam Cochran 懷疑，CommEx 似乎是透過早期產品 Binance Cloud (幣安雲) 運行，這能讓合作的交易所共享幣安的流動性。</p><p>Adam Cochran 認為，這解釋了為什麼 CommEx 僅上線幾小時就已經有上百萬美元的交易量。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">6/25</p><p>That explains how this day 1 site has $1M in volume on BTC/UST with healthy bid spread on both sides of the market despite launching five hours ago. <a href="https://t.co/vBvyEKSjzu">pic.twitter.com/vBvyEKSjzu</a></p><p>— Adam Cochran (adamscochran.eth) (@adamscochran) <a href="https://twitter.com/adamscochran/status/1707052170053353535?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 27, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="CommEx_%E5%90%88%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%99%E6%BA%96%E4%BD%8E%E8%90%BD"></span><strong>CommEx 合規標準低落</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>面對質疑，幣安發言人向外媒 <a href="https://cointelegraph.com/news/crypto-binance-successor-russia-commex-exchange" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cointelegraph</a> 表示，俄羅斯幣安的用戶能自由選擇是否使用 CommEx。</p><p>據瞭解，CommEx 的合規標準相當低，無需 KYC 即能有 2BTC 的出金額度。</p><figure id="attachment_79913" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-79913" style="width: 392px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-79913 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2-2023-09-28-150620.png?resize=392%2C623&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="392" height="623" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-150620.png?w=392&amp;ssl=1 392w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-150620.png?resize=189%2C300&amp;ssl=1 189w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-150620.png?resize=378%2C600&amp;ssl=1 378w" sizes="(max-width: 392px) 100vw, 392px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-79913" class="wp-caption-text">CommEx 官網</figcaption></figure><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="CommEx_%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E9%81%B8%E9%A0%85%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C"></span><strong>CommEx 支付選項包括被制裁銀行</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>此外，CommEx 在<a href="https://commex.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/7831162016783-CommEX-Location-Restrictions" target="_blank" rel="noopener">地區限制</a>中也排除了美國、新加坡等國家。</p><p>根據其 P2P 交易介面，支付選項包括了被制裁的俄羅斯銀行 Sberbank 。</p><p>CommEx 發言人在 <a href="https://t.me/CommEX_RUChat/1349" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TG</a> 回應用戶時表示，平台註冊於塞席爾 (Seychelles)，專注於獨立國家聯合體 (CIS) 及亞洲地區。</p><p><strong>(回顧報導：<a href="https://abmedia.io/20220303-eu-announces-seven-bank-kick-out-from-swift" target="_blank" rel="noopener">歐盟公佈俄羅斯 7 銀行逐出 SWIFT，制裁範圍包括加密貨幣與白俄羅斯</a>)</strong></p><figure id="attachment_79915" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-79915" style="width: 1193px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="wp-image-79915 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2-2023-09-28-150058.png?resize=1193%2C434&amp;ssl=1" alt="" width="1193" height="434" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-150058.png?w=1193&amp;ssl=1 1193w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-150058.png?resize=300%2C109&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-150058.png?resize=1024%2C373&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-150058.png?resize=600%2C218&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-09-28-150058.png?resize=768%2C279&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-79915" class="wp-caption-text">P2P 交易介面</figcaption></figure><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="%E8%B6%99%E9%95%B7%E9%B5%AC%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%EF%BC%9A%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E9%A1%9E%E4%BC%BC%E6%98%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%86%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E9%AB%94%E9%A9%97"></span><strong>趙長鵬回應：設計類似是為了用戶體驗</strong><span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>CZ 表示幣安之前負責獨立國家聯合體 (CIS) 的成員可能會，或已經加入 CommEx，他認為這是件好事。</p><p>之所以要求 CommEx 的設計、API 皆與幣安類似，則是為了確保流暢的用戶體驗。</p><p>CZ 特別強調，包括 Mercedes、麥當勞等企業在俄羅斯出售時都保有回購選項，但幣安的情況完全不同，幣安不會獲得任何持續的收入分潤，也不保留以任何方式回購業務股份的選項。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Some answers about Binance/CommEx.</p><p>There will be crypto transfers between Binance &amp; CommEx as users migrate with their funds. There are also older transactions during the testing phase of the integrations. This is expected.</p><p>A few ex-Binance CIS team members may join their team,…</p><p>— CZ 🔶 Binance (@cz_binance) <a href="https://twitter.com/cz_binance/status/1707293387001307551?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 28, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p></p>
]]>
